plss use magnet link
sorry for the inconvenience

Really great program! You can convert to lots of different files. Many options, fast conversions.

If you make music in guitar pro and/or want to practice individual tracks from other bands you can select individual tracks and just convert everything and exclude the guitars, take the mp3's with you to practise anywhere. Its awesome. The finished converted files sounds a bit more real than midi, like GP's RSE.

Thanks for the upload, you rock!
